data.description: SELLER WILL PAY OFF SOLAR PANELS TO BE OWNED! MOTIVATED SELLER ALL OFFERS ARE WELCOME. Take a look at this beautiful 2 story build from 2017 like new and well maintained home. The home has ALOT of space with open kitchen and family room  floor plans. The LOFT is perfect for additional entertainment space. The home is equipped with a private den for an office or an additional bedroom. The backyard is immaculate with pavers and upgrades! This home is ready to accommodate your BUYERS needs! Conveniently located by the 101 freeway, 303 freeway, US60 Grand for easy transit throughout the valley. Easy access to Westgate , Arrowhead mall, and Park West for dining shopping and entertainment.
